author: Phil Helsel
title: Navy hospital ship USNS Mercy to arrive in Los Angeles Friday
description: The Navy hospital ship USNS Mercy is set to arrive in Los Angeles on Friday, where it will help ease the burden on health systems so that hospitals can care for COVID-19 patients.
content:
The Navy hospital ship USNS Mercy is expected to arrive in Los Angeles on Friday to support medical systems amid the coronavirus epidemic.
